title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - Sim Update VI - released
description:
Asobo has just released Sim Update VI besides a lot of fixes for both scenery, airplanes, weather and VR a nice surprise has been added to MSFS 2020. Several POI's have been illuminated in Windows 11 colors to celebrate the release of Windows 11. In addition to this a special livery has been added to the  EXTRA 330LT.
